Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment across all variants containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that include Completed + In Call versus variants that end in Completed + Resolved -> Completed + Closed without Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment when it appears before Accepted + Wait - User compared to when it appears before Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Time from the start of Queued + Awaiting Assignment to the occurrence of Completed + In Call in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the next occurrence of Completed + In Call within the same process instance
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average cycle time of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in cases where Completed + In Call occurs at least once
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that transition directly to Accepted + In Progress versus those that loop back to Queued + Awaiting Assignment before reaching Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Time of Queued + Awaiting Assignment when it is immediately followed by Accepted + In Progress and later leads to Completed + In Call, compared to when it leads to Completed + Resolved -> Completed + Closed without any wait states
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'
